column19: * Some unusual results - in that the sub samples
in some cases were heavier than the whole sample (FW)
I have been able to allow in most cases for a tared bag left
on the balance, or if the Fresh sub weight was just a gram or two out
then I have adjusted to FW.
As a note it was fairly windy during weighing on the field and there was often
a problem with the signal between computer and balance (not talking)
If in doubt - disregard any samples which have an added comment
in the Fresh/ sub weights as these are where I have noted any
Another thing to consider - some difference between weights of plastic bags?
